```json
{
  "application": "Bash",
  "details": {
    "dependencies": [
      "Idr.calc_rescue_and_selfconsist_ratio.sh"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "files": [
        "rep1_lib.txt",
        "rep2_lib.txt",
        "control1_lib.txt",
        "control2_lib.txt",
        "ALL_TF_FILE_NAME",
        "$REP1_FILE_NAME",
        "$REP2_FILE_NAME",
        "$CONTROL1_FILE_NAME",
        "$CONTROL2_FILE_NAME"
      ],
      "directories": [
        "/gpfs/gpfs1/home/schhetri/python",
        "/gpfs/gpfs1/home/snewberry/interrupt/encode/spp_and_idr/idr_testing",
        "$BASE_DIR/IDR_${R1}_${R2}"
      ]
    },
    "environment variables": [
      "BASE_DIR",
      "RUN_PATH",
      "RATIO_OUTPUT_DIR"
    ],
    "commands": [
      "source /gpfs/gpfs1/home/schhetri/python/anaconda_python_version3.sh",
      "source activate python3",
      "mkdir $RATIO_OUTPUT_DIR",
      "readarray LIB_REP1 < $REP1_FILE_NAME",
      "readarray LIB_REP2 < $REP2_FILE_NAME",
      "readarray LIB_CONTROL1 < $CONTROL1_FILE_NAME",
      "readarray LIB_CONTROL2 < $CONTROL2_FILE_NAME",
      "readarray ALL_LIB < $ALL_TF_FILE_NAME",
      "echo ${LIB_REP1[@]} | tr \" \" \"\\n\" | tr \"\\n\" \" \"",
      "echo ${LIB_REP2[@]} | tr \" \" \"\\n\" | tr \"\\n\" \" \"",
      "echo ${LIB_CONTROL1[@]} | tr \" \" \"\\n\" | tr \"\\n\" \" \"",
      "echo ${LIB_CONTROL2[@]} | tr \" \" \"\\n\" | tr \"\\n\" \" \"",
      "echo ${ALL_LIB[@]} | tr \" \" \"\\n\" | sort -u | tr \"\\n\" \" \"",
      "$RUN_PATH/Idr.calc_rescue_and_selfconsist_ratio.sh $Nt_IDR_THRESHOLD_FILE $Np_IDR_THRESHOLD_FILE $N1_IDR_THRESHOLD_FILE $N2_IDR_THRESHOLD_FILE $IDR_DIR/${R1}_${R2}_rescue_and_self_consistency_ratio.txt"
    ],
    "script purpose": "This script appears to process IDR (Irreproducible Discovery Rate) results from chromatin immunoprecipitation sequencing (ChIP-seq) experiments."
  }
}
```
